text: == Events == * First Council of the Lateran confirms Concordat of Worms and demands that priests remain celibate. * End of the reign of Emperor Toba, emperor of Japan. * Emperor Sutoku ascends to the throne of Japan. * St Bartholomew's Hospital (Barts) founded in London, England. * The Pactum Warmundi is established between the Republic of Venice and the Kingdom of Jerusalem. == Births == * Minamoto no Yoshitomo, Japanese general (d. 1160) * Leonardo Fibonacci, Mathematician born (d. 1209) == Deaths == * August 29 â€” Eystein I of Norway (b. around 1088) * Wanyan Aguda, chieftain of the Jurchen Wanyan tribe (b. 1068) * Peter of Pappacarbone
